Enum Class PropertyType

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<PropertyType>
Objects.PropertyType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<PropertyType>, Constable
public enum PropertyType extends Enum<PropertyType>
Enumerates the available property types and their price multipliers. Each multiplier affects the final nightly price of a reservation.
